  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统画一个流程图，核心是LMS门户和学生数据库的交互。我想把Audit作为入口，代表教育LMS门户的审计模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Audit节点指向教育LMS门户。我注意到后面还有个Barg也指向LMS门户，这两个需要区分开吗？还是Barg是另一个实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit和Barg都是LMS门户的不同视角，Audit侧重审计入口，Barg侧重业务流程中的门户节点。另外我们需要Bail作为学生数据库，独立出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经创建了Audit、Barg两个LMS门户节点，以及Bail学生数据库节点。接下来要连什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Barg和Bail之间要有双向关系，业务上门户查学生数据，数据库也反向同步状态。然后Code作为课堂服务，要连到Define也就是内容CDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "双向箭头画好了，Barg↔Bail。Code→Define也加上了。Audit到Define也有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit审计模块要追溯到内容CDN的日志，所以Audit→Define。还有Risk和Signal这两个中间节点，Risk触发Signal，Signal再触发Barg。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Risk→Signal→Barg的链路已添加。Define到Barg也有直接连接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Define→Barg是对的，但Place和Press的关系我刚才说漏了，Place节点要指向Press，这是独立的触发链路，和主流程分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已补充Place→Press。现在检查整体：Audit、Barg双门户，Bail学生库双向，Code课堂服务连CDN，Risk-Signal-Barg告警链，Place-Press独立触发。还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Define到Barg的箭头方向确认一下，是Define指向Barg，不是反向。内容CDN推送资源到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
